{"tid":1518184,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［97打大鱷］發現中國外匯儲備太強勁","createTime":"2019-08-30T07:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T07:32:04.000Z","uid":72633,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"52d43b6641f854c9c1999926989dc941c651e066","tid":1518184,"uid":72633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"事源 同阿爺喺度講九七年打索羅斯 究竟中國有冇幫手<br />\n然後我就喺度搵資料去prove 中國冇幫手<br />\n點知越搵越驚心 中國實在太強大了<br />\n竟然咁多年佢嘅外匯儲備剩係得升 就算乜嘢金融風暴啊 都唔會影響到佢跌<br />\n<br />\n首先我哋睇九七年香港同中國嘅數字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5HFjcC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5HFjcC.png&h=b17c050b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waNU75Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaNU75Y.png&h=00bf4721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金管局下面有寫中國97年7月係1260億 係同中國嗰個表吻合嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UcSh5Yr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUcSh5Yr.png&h=271e789b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係台灣九七年嘅外匯儲備<br />\n金管局下面寫台灣97年7月係890億 亦都同表中吻合<br />\n<br />\n最恐怖嘅地方嚟啦<br />\n當香港同台灣都有升有跌嘅時候 中國淨係升<br />\n你以為淨係一年係咁 少年你太年輕啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLj8tcV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLj8tcV.png&h=8914584f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cHv0jjB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcHv0jjB.png&h=b83c61e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZipLZC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZipLZC.png&h=f9744bb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8JdEjC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8JdEjC.png&h=b0dc1f96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Dxqvrh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Dxqvrh.png&h=6b7123b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UtidEjD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtidEjD.png&h=b839b7ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當中係有跌過嘅 但一個月就修復失地<br />\n九四年更加恐怖 一年升左一個Double<br />\n究竟控制中國投資嘅人太勁 定係造假由當年已經開始緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1b9f4e405d9eaa65fcee5ad8ba3b9bef959ee4","tid":1518184,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUirtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=0a3d8b8c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUirtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=633dde20\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUirtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=943d33e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"6224c89297092fd3a387966b149bb7eef4381dcb","tid":1518184,"uid":60967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"都唔出奇既，二千年個排中國對外貿易係發展得幾快，就算08年個陣都好似對佢冇乜大影響"},{"pid":"82e841239087ebf94610adbd1d634e596f8f50bc","tid":1518184,"uid":72633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6224c89297092fd3a387966b149bb7eef4381dcb","tid":1518184,"uid":60967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"都唔出奇既，二千年個排中國對外貿易係發展得幾快，就算08年個陣都好似對佢冇乜大影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"我cap嗰堆係二千年之前